ice for each group). One-way ANOVA followed by Tukey’s multiple comparisons test. O Adipose tissue Has2 expression from mice treated with 0.2% or 5% 4-MU HFHS (n = 6 mice for control group, n = 7 mice for 0.2% 4-MU and 5% 4-MU). One-way ANOVA followed by Tukey’s multiple comparisons test. All data are presented as mean ± s.e.m. *indicates p ≤ 0.05, **indicates p ≤ 0.01.
